archimate:Contract.name: 3 Protected User Information Policy (Contract)
archimate:Contract.documentation:
Scientific data and operational metadata reserved for authorized data consumers, who are normally outside the project. The risks associated with accidental disclosures of small fractions of Protected User data are small. The risks of large or routine, or malevolent disclosure of Protected User data are significant.
EXAMPLES: ● Released LSST Level 2 data products ● User-generated Level 3 data products ● Certain operational metadata that discloses research topics of end users, for example, queries
